OL,3,CNew 'quiet lanes' to be rolled out
OL,4,Cacross Oxfordshire as part of pilot
OL,5,Cscheme
OL,7,FNew quiet lanes are to be introduced
OL,8,Facross Oxfordshire to make it safer
OL,9,Ffor pedestrians.
OL,11,FThe pilot scheme, which has been
OL,12,Fapproved by Oxfordshire County Council
OL,13,F(OCC), will restrict traffic on some
OL,14,Froads.
OL,16,FIt's hoped the lanes will reduce
OL,17,Fvehicle numbers and speeds, and cut
OL,18,Fthe risk of collisions.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
