PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1779789943
OL,3,CNew 'quiet lanes' to be rolled out
OL,4,Cacross Oxfordshire as part of pilot
OL,5,Cscheme
OL,7,FThe authority has said it will only
OL,8,Fintroduce them where there is strong
OL,9,Flocal support and a suitable
OL,10,Falternative route for traffic.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FThey will all include physical
OL,18,Fmeasures to stop traffic - such as
OL,19,Fgates and bollards - quiet lane
OL,20,Fsignage and speed limit changes.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
