PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1779789943
OL,3,CNew 'quiet lanes' to be rolled out
OL,4,Cacross Oxfordshire as part of pilot
OL,5,Cscheme
OL,7,FAny speed limit reductions will
OL,8,Ftypically fall to 20 miles per hour.
OL,10,FOCC Councillor Rebekah Fletcher,
OL,11,FCabinet Member for Transport
OL,12,FManagement, said: "Quiet lanes are
OL,13,Fabout making sure local roads work for
OL,14,Fthe communities that live there, not
OL,15,Fas cut-throughs for traffic they were
OL,16,Fnever designed to carry.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
